feat: enforce project-level access via team_projects (fl-wmd.2)

Add requireProjectAccess middleware that checks team-based project
visibility for all project-scoped API endpoints. Owners and admins
bypass the check. Members and viewers are restricted to projects
linked to their teams via team_projects. The listProjects endpoint
now filters results by the caller's access.

